  "subject": "Support decoding of PdpGroups from a string",
  "commit_message": "Support decoding of PdpGroups from a string\n\nTo use PdpGroups as a @PathParam in the new \"delete-policies-from-group\"\nAPI in PAP, it must have a fromString static method.  Added such a method,\nwhich takes either a JSON or a YAML string.\n\nChange-Id: I165f93a29550542373bc5cce15dac8a9aa413037\nIssue-ID: POLICY-2274\nSigned-off-by: Jim Hahn <jrh3@att.com>\n",
